Release Notes
-----------------------------------------------------------------

When Ben receives a call from his old flame, Lulu his calm life is turned upside down. Lulu 

takes Ben on a whirlwind road trip where he discovers that life is a crazy ride.

Lulu (Melanie Griffith of WORKING GIRL and SOMETHING WILD) has always been a wild 

woman--spontaneous, adventurous, and charming, the lovely blonde lives up to her hair color. 

An impulsive call to her ex-boyfriend Ben (DIRTY DANCING's hunky Patrick Swayze) ends up in 

a cross-country road trip on which anything can happen, and many of them do! An 

unconventional, inspiring romance, ALONG FOR THE RIDE also stars Penelope Ann Miller and 

Joseph Gordon-Levitt. 




